relation: Twinkling lights to adorn your Frostfell tree!
pageTitle: Feelin' Gifty in New Halas! :: Quests :: EverQuest II :: ZAM
textBeforeTable: The Gigglegibber goblin was very happy with my assistance, and has granted me the ability to adorn the Frostfell tree that Gh'lad Tydingz rewarded me with. I delivered all the gifts to the right citizens! I spoke to G'shugahplum. Complete: Return to G'shugahplum in New Halas. Start: Stage 4Whether the gifts went to the person that G'shugahplum had intended, I do not know. I should now return to G'shugahplum. I have delivered all of the gifts that were given to me. I gave a gift to Glip Mightblade. Complete: Deliver a gift to Glip Mightblade. Start: I gave a gift to Virginia Strongarms. Complete: Deliver a gift to Virginia Strongarms. Start: I gave a gift to Kendi Wiggletail. Complete: Deliver a gift to Kendi Wiggletail. Start: I gave a gift to Kalib Mal. Complete: Deliver a gift to Kalib Mal. Start: I gave a gift to Marcus Angelfire. Complete: Deliver a gift
